      "content": "thanks, i'll let them know. honestly though, some of the senior execs are a bit nervous about this move. they're worried that relying on human \"consultants\" might make our forecasts too subjective or driven by political correctness rather than actual market data. what's your take on how a human team compares to your data-driven approach for predicting shifts?",
